de.interactive_instruments.etf.dal.dto

Class Dto

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.interactive_instruments.etf.dal.dto.Dto
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.interactive_instruments.Copyable<Dto>, EidHolder, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AttachmentDto, ModelItemDto, TranslationArgumentCollectionDto

    public abstract class Dto
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable, EidHolder, de.interactive_instruments.Copyable<Dto>
    Abstract Data Transfer Object for the ETF model which is used as a simple container to carry data between the different ETF layers and processes. A DTO does not contain any business logic but may implement internal consistency checks and basic validations.
